                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Attius <lb n="2"/>Propinqui <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>ertus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Senno <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LX <lb n="4"/>et Elvia Oclatius <lb n="5"/>et Finita <expan><abbr>con</abbr><ex>iux</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1: hedera. Z. 4: Spuren einer Tilgung, ursprünglich stand dort: et Elviae con(iugi). Noch Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben erhalten.</p>
            </div>
